metadata.name: Exodia The Forbidden One 1/64
metadata.description:
This NFT represents fractional ownership of a Gem Mint 1st Edition Exodia The Forbidden One from Yu-Gi-Oh's Legend of Blue Eyes. Upon sale of the set via the purchase() function, owners of these NFTs can call claim() on the contract to receive their share of the total sales price.

Ownership of this NFT does not constitute ownership of the copyright in the drawing incorporated in the work associated with the NFT.

Hover thumbnail or visit https://mannys.game/dao/assets/forbidden-one to see full asset.
